{"tid":2437461,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"瑞士公投通過禁止公共地方蒙面","createTime":"2021-03-08T01:38:01.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-08T12:45:42.000Z","uid":61257,"like":52,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"6d832ade62cdf8d71312205ac14287e8314cc7b9","tid":2437461,"uid":61257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T01:38:01.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】瑞士舉行公投，通過禁止在公共地方蒙面，包括禁止穆斯林女性穿罩袍的提案。<br />\n<br />\n當局公布初步點票結果，有百分之51.2選票支持公投提案，比反對的多2.4個百分點，今次公投沒有提及伊斯蘭教，只是倡議禁止民眾在公共地方蒙面，但被外界稱為「禁罩袍公投」。<br />\n<br />\n有份提出公投的瑞士人民黨議員，之前亦表明蒙面是極端伊斯蘭政治的象徵。<br />\n<br />\n今次公投通過後，瑞士政府要在兩年內制訂法例，但當地的穆斯林團體表明，將會對今次公投結果提出法律挑戰。"},{"pid":"9f991169dd43dc0c59e9ca5f1ae8541dfa259046","tid":2437461,"uid":231480,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T01:39:46.000Z","msg":"港共表示<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7a688248c8cb37b4cbc3a93390700b6272f6c09","tid":2437461,"uid":157994,"like":46,"dislike":1,"score":45,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T02:04:31.000Z","msg":"伊斯蘭文化入侵歐洲 真係近代史上最大笑話<br />\n好彩有鬼佬發現唔對路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0aef3898df9e21e85cee672cfe359a8e655ce10","tid":2437461,"uid":82938,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c7a688248c8cb37b4cbc3a93390700b6272f6c09","tid":2437461,"uid":157994,"like":46,"dislike":1,"score":45,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T02:04:31.000Z","msg":"伊斯蘭文化入侵歐洲 真係近代史上最大笑話<br />\n好彩有鬼佬發現唔對路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T04:51:08.000Z","msg":"點睇都似禁示威蒙面下話<br />\n<br />\n中立國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c0251b512680ac07b834e6ea886bed01cc4adcd","tid":2437461,"uid":179409,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"quote":{"pid":"9f991169dd43dc0c59e9ca5f1ae8541dfa259046","tid":2437461,"uid":231480,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-08